    "He suffered a series of strokes in the retirement home and died at age 82.": [],
    "Nearly all of his books were enlarged and reissued by himself.": [],
    "Richardson's <em>Painting in American</em> has largely been superseded by later books which incorporate women, minority and non-Western-tradition art.": [],
    "However, his book stands among the first to seriously look at documentary evidence for American art as a principal of evaluation.": []
